<template>
  <v-btn
    v-if="un_communicate"
    icon
    color="pink"
    @click="handleDeleteCommunication(communication_subordinate)"
  >
    <v-icon>mdi-heart</v-icon>
  </v-btn>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "UnCommunication",
  components: {},

  props: {
    communication_subordinate: {
      type: Object,
      required: true,
    },
    un_communicate: {
      type: Boolean,
      required: true,
    },
  },

  computed: {},

  created() {},

  methods: {
    handleDeleteCommunication(communication_subordinate) {
      this.$emit("delete-communication", communication_subordinate);
      this.un_communicate = false;
    },
  },
};
</script>

<style scoped></style>
